00:21:19.219 --> 00:21:20.419
Is that really going to work?

00:21:20.419 --> 00:21:23.499
No, no, no, they just did it.

00:21:23.499 --> 00:21:25.739
V. 8, Jesus then said to them,

00:21:25.739 --> 00:21:28.019
draw out now and bear it

00:21:28.019 --> 00:21:30.979
