00:21:30.979 --> 00:21:34.339
And they bear it.

00:21:34.339 --> 00:21:35.659
There's no questioning.

00:21:35.659 --> 00:21:37.379
There's no discussion.

00:21:37.379 --> 00:21:39.019
They just did it.

00:21:39.019 --> 00:21:42.099
They heard what Mary said.

00:21:42.099 --> 00:21:45.339
Whatsoever He saith unto you, do it.

00:21:45.339 --> 00:21:48.339
We come to v. 9 of John 2,

00:21:48.339 --> 00:21:50.059
