00:21:53.819 --> 00:21:57.179
look at this phrase, this parenthesis.

00:21:57.179 --> 00:22:02.899
It says, but the servants which drew the water knew.

00:22:02.899 --> 00:22:04.739
Isn't that good?

00:22:04.739 --> 00:22:07.539
See, they heard Mary say

00:22:07.539 --> 00:22:11.019
whatsoever He saith unto you, do it.

00:22:11.019 --> 00:22:13.459
When we go to the Word of God,

00:22:13.459 --> 00:22:16.859
we just need to have a hard attitude of obedience.

00:22:16.859 --> 00:22:20.979
You know, there's a phraseology,

00:22:21.179 --> 00:22:23.979
a logo, just do it,

00:22:23.979 --> 00:22:27.099
within the sports arena.

00:22:27.099 --> 00:22:29.459
We come to the truth of this thought

00:22:29.459 --> 00:22:33.059
in John 2, do it.

00:22:33.059 --> 00:22:34.659
Just obey.

00:22:34.659 --> 00:22:37.099
And that's exactly what we see Moses doing here

00:22:37.099 --> 00:22:39.379
in Exodus 40.

00:22:39.379 --> 00:22:41.619
And thou shalt.

00:22:41.619 --> 00:22:43.659
And thou shalt.

00:22:43.659 --> 00:22:47.659
And, I mean, just repeated, repeated, repeated, repeated.

00:22:47.659 --> 00:22:50.939
God has given specific instruction

00:22:50.939 --> 00:22:52.619
and then the Bible says,

00:22:52.619 --> 00:22:53.939
thus did Moses,

00:22:53.939 --> 00:22:59.619
