00:23:14.499 --> 00:23:16.459
And thou shalt.

00:23:16.459 --> 00:23:19.659
What happens between and thou shalt

00:23:19.699 --> 00:23:23.179
and then is obedience.

00:23:23.179 --> 00:23:27.659
And you only get then if you obey.

00:23:27.659 --> 00:23:29.379
And that's what Moses did.

00:23:29.379 --> 00:23:30.419
Moses obeyed.

00:23:30.419 --> 00:23:33.259
Then, the result of the behavior,

00:23:33.259 --> 00:23:37.059
the event that is recorded,

00:23:37.059 --> 00:23:38.099
the Bible says,

00:23:38.099 --> 00:23:43.059
